      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i've already talked to the floor staff and they're pretty sure they're being careful. we also checked for logging lags in the WMS, but everything seems synced up. \n\nit's just weird, it's always just a few units here and there, specifically these small electronic components. nothing major, just enough to mess up our precision counts. do you think there could be something else, like maybe a unit of measure error or something with how they're being scanned?",
